      "author": "magnitus99",
      "description": "## Changes\n\n- Load all models returned by OpenAI-compatible providers instead of filtering out embedding-capable models.\n- Support custom OpenAI-compatible providers for RAG embeddings.\n- Use Obsidian requestUrl for OpenAI-compatible embedding generation to avoid CORS failures.\n- Store plugin settings in device-local Obsidian local storage and migrate legacy data.json settings.\n- Raise the minimum Obsidian version to 1.8.7 for local storage support.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/magnitus99/Superpower-Inside/compare/1.0.16...1.0.17",
